S_{n} = \operatorname{tr}(A^{n})
 A  = \begin{bmatrix} 3 + \sqrt{5} & 0\\ 0 & 3 - \sqrt{5} \end{bmatrix} 
 A^{2} - 6 A + 4 = 0 
 A^{n+2} - 6 A^{n+1} + 4 A^{n} = 0. 
